===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|automatique|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|αὐτόματον|tr=automaton|lang=grc}}, neuter of {{term|αὐτόματος||self-moving, moving of oneself, self-acting, spontaneous|tr=automatos|lang=grc}}, from {{term|αὐτός||self, myself|tr=autos|lang=grc}} + {{term|μέμαα||to wish eagerly, strive, yearn, desire|tr=memaa|lang=grc}}.

